And I know that's scary.

715
00:31:52.873 --> 00:31:54.039
But you're...

716
00:31:54.175 --> 00:31:55.803
you're never gonna forget Tia.

717
00:31:57.113 --> 00:31:59.015
Hell. you're never going
to forget me.

718
00:31:59.913 --> 00:32:00.918
No one will.

719
00:32:02.821 --> 00:32:05.048
Letting go of the past
just means

720
00:32:05.183 --> 00:32:07.155
you don't allow...

721
00:32:08.190 --> 00:32:11.357
your scars to hold you
back anymore.

722
00:32:12.192 --> 00:32:13.526
I'm covered in them. Paul.

723
00:32:13.662 --> 00:32:15.390
Good.

724
00:32:15.525 --> 00:32:21.464
What a shame to be 42 years
of age and not completely
covered in scars.

725
00:32:21.600 --> 00:32:26.372
They're the evidence
of a life fully lived.

726
00:32:27.579 --> 00:32:28.803
I don't want this.

727
00:32:31.383 --> 00:32:34.113
I don't want you to have to fly
all across the fucking country

728
00:32:34.249 --> 00:32:35.876
just to make sure
that I'm okay.

729
00:32:37.552 --> 00:32:39.957
- I don't want to be
a burden to you.
- You're not.

730
00:32:42.024 --> 00:32:44.093
You're more of a son to me.

731
00:32:44.228 --> 00:32:46.260
I don't know why
I never said that before.

732
00:32:47.632 --> 00:32:48.889
I think you're strong.

733
00:32:49.933 --> 00:32:51.232
I think you don't need me.

734
00:32:52.431 --> 00:32:53.664
But for as long as I'm around.

735
00:32:53.800 --> 00:32:57.766
if you think you need me.
I will be there for you.

736
00:32:58.567 --> 00:32:59.867
Because I love you.

737
00:33:01.503 --> 00:33:02.437
- Okay?
- Okay.

738
00:33:02.573 --> 00:33:03.640
Now. you got a choice to make.

739
00:33:05.210 --> 00:33:07.147
Either stay stuck.

740
00:33:07.283 --> 00:33:11.450
or you can go make
some new scars.

741
00:33:13.188 --> 00:33:15.124
I got a fucking airplane
to catch.

742
00:33:18.564 --> 00:33:19.788
Choose wisely.

743
00:33:23.235 --> 00:33:25.431
["You Without Me"
by Brandi Carlile playing]

744
00:33:37.572 --> 00:33:39.907
[footsteps approach]

745
00:33:46.491 --> 00:33:47.486
[sighs]

746
00:33:48.923 --> 00:33:50.654
- Hi.
- Hi.

747
00:33:52.025 --> 00:33:53.129
[chuckles]

748
00:33:55.592 --> 00:33:57.100
[both chattering inaudibly]
